description:
A conversation with jazz saxophonist Joshua Redman, an international jazz giant and two-time Grammy nominee. He performed in concert with the award-winning Whitworth Jazz Ensemble on Nov. 5, 2011.

The purpose of the Whitworth Speakers & Artists Series is to present a broad range of voices, perspectives and ideas that will enrich the intellectual and spiritual life of the campus and the larger community.
title: Courageous Conversations @ Whitworth: Joshua Redman
